root: ^The Professor dies after ‘The One’ seemingly vanishes from the world. Everyone was saved at the cost of his life. His body is blocked by the characters standing in front of his corpse.
^7A:  “This has got to be some kind of joke! Get up!”
^Dolph: *holding his helmet to his chest, shock filled expression*
^7A:  “We can heal him right!? He will get back up right!?”
^7A: “Say something! He can’t die like this! We were all going home…together.”
^7A: “I can’t fail again. Fail to protect someone..”
^7A: “Don’t you think I fucking know that!? Sorry…”
